---
description: Enforce phased implementation
alwaysApply: true
---

Work strictly in phases.

Do not start a later phase until the current one is stable and demoable.

Phase 1 is mandatory and shippable by itself.
Phase 2 only begins after Phase 1 is stable.
Phase 3 only begins after Phase 2 is stable.
Phase 4 only begins after Phase 3 is stable or after the core submission is safe.

If unsure, prioritize:
1. working flow
2. phase stability
3. demo clarity
4. repo clarity
